    "body": "fixes #9160 \r\nfixes #909 \r\nfixes #639\r\n\r\nThis PR adds a new entry in `config.yaml`:\r\n```yaml\r\nconfig:\r\n   shared_linking: 'rpath'\r\n```\r\nIf this variable is set to `rpath` (the default) Spack will set RPATH in ELF binaries. If set to `runpath` it will set RUNPATH.",
